Interface DefaultPhaseOne

All Known Implementing Classes:
PhaseOneImpl
public interface DefaultPhaseOne

BEL compiler phase one interface.

Phase one consists of XXX stages, executed in sequence. The output of phase one is a proto-network.

Method Detail

stage1XBELValidation

DefaultPhaseOne.Stage1Output stage1XBELValidation(File f)
Executes stage one validation of an XBEL file.

This stage consists of:

  1. Syntactic validation of the file against the XBEL schema
  2. Conversion of the JAXB-based XML model to the common model (defined by both BELModelObject and BELObject)
  3. Syntactic validation of the converted model against its external resources

Parameters:
f - XBEL XML file
Returns:
A non-null list of validation errors
Throws:
ValidationError - Thrown if the file fails validation

stage1BELValidation

DefaultPhaseOne.Stage1Output stage1BELValidation(File f)
Executes stage one validation of a BEL file.

This stage consists of:

  1. Syntactic validation of the BEL file by executing the BELParser
  2. Conversion of the BELScript model to the common model (defined by both BELModelObject and BELObject)
  3. Syntactic validation of the converted model against its external resources

Parameters:
f - File, the BELScript file
Returns:
A non-null list of validation errors
Throws:
ValidationError - Thrown if the file fails validation

Executes stage two namespace compilation of a BEL document.

This stage consists of:

Throws:

ResourceDownloadError - Thrown if an error occurred downloading a namespace

stage4SemanticVerification

void stage4SemanticVerification(Document d)
                                throws SemanticFailure,
                                       IndexingFailure
Executes stage four semantic verification of a BEL document.

This stage consists of:

  1. Semantic verification of parameters
  2. Semantic verification of terms
  3. Semantic verification of statements

Parameters:
d - BEL document
Throws:
SemanticFailure - Thrown when a semantic failure occurs verifying the provided document or an error occurred during the verification process
IndexingFailure - Thrown if a term parameter's namespace could not be accessed

stage6Expansion

void stage6Expansion(Document doc,
                     ProtoNetwork pn,
                     boolean stmtExpand)
Executes stage six expansion of a BEL document.

This stage consists of:

  1. Expansion of statements
  2. Expansion of terms

This stage modifies the proto network by adding additional proto nodes and proto edges.

Parameters:
doc - the original document needed as a dependency when using proto network builder
pn - the proto network to modify
stmtExpand - determines if proto network statements should be expanded to proto edges by inferring relationships
